OL,3,CMan jailed for raping child at party
OL,5,FA man has been jailed for nine years
OL,6,Ffor raping a child at a party.
OL,8,FThe victim was given alcohol by 32-
OL,9,Fyear-old Ammar Moqbal - a stranger -
OL,10,Fbefore it happened, Sheffield Crown
OL,11,FCourt heard.
OL,13,FThe youngster left the party and
OL,14,Fapproached a member of the public
OL,15,Fasking for help.
OL,17,FIt was reported to the police and
OL,18,FMoqbal was arrested and charged with
OL,19,Frape of a child aged 13/14/15.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/4
