PN,36402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1772745125
OL,3,CMan jailed for raping child at party
OL,5,FHe pleaded not guilty but was found
OL,6,Fguilty by a jury in October 2025.
OL,7,FMoqbal, of Exter Driver, Sheffield,
OL,8,Fwas given a nine-year sentence.
OL,10,FDuring the court hearing, the victim's
OL,11,Faccount was read out.
OL,13,FIt said, "What happened to me that
OL,14,Fnight has affected each and every part
OL,15,Fof my life.
OL,17,F"That night I was with my friends and
OL,18,Fcould have never known what was about
OL,19,Fto happen. I found myself in a
OL,20,Fsituation I could not control and as a
OL,21,Fchild could not see a way out of.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/4
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,365,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1772745125
OL,3,CMan jailed for raping child at party
OL,5,F"I lost the normality of just being in
OL,6,Fschool. I couldn't concentrate on my
OL,7,Fwork or studies, as there was not
OL,8,Fenough head space for me to deal with
OL,9,Fthe trauma I suffered, as well as what
OL,10,Fothers were saying to me.
OL,12,FIt continued, "I think the best way to
OL,13,Fdescribe my state of mind now, is
OL,14,Fsimilar to suffering a bereavement.
OL,15,FIt's like I am grieving for the life I
OL,16,Ffeel I have lost. I worry that one day
OL,17,Fthese all of these things will
OL,18,Fovercome me.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/4
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,365,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1772745125
OL,3,CMan jailed for raping child at party
OL,5,F"I can't and will not allow this to
OL,6,Fhappen. I will not let those who
OL,7,Fharmed me win, that time is done."
OL,9,FThree men who were also charged with
OL,10,Frape of a child aged 13/14/15 were
OL,11,Ffound not guilty by a jury in February
OL,12,F2024 they were released with no
OL,13,Ffurther action.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/4
